ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.property

Class PropertyHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.usask.simlab.odeToJava.property.PropertyHolder

  • public class PropertyHolder
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the central data structure in ODEToJava that is responsible for holding all the properties used by solvers and their modules.
